Class OldSwedishCurrency

  • java.lang.Object
    • OldSwedishCurrency

  • public class OldSwedishCurrency
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines Old Swedish Currency objects Each OSC will hold an amount of riksdaler, skilling and runstycken.

    The Old Swedish Currency works as follows:

    1 riksdaler = 48 skilling = 768 runstycken.

    1 skilling = 16 runstycken = 1/48 riksdaler.

    1 runstycken = 1/16 skilling = 1/768 riksdaler.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Luis Saravia Patron
